      h3 Features
      p Sidekiq Pro contains the following functionality:
      ul
        li Enable more complex job workflows with Batches and Callbacks
        li Better server reliability in the face of Ruby VM crashes
        li Better client reliability in the face of Redis networking problems
        li Pause queues (e.g. only process a queue during business hours)
        li Expire unprocessed jobs after a deadline
        li Send job processing metrics to Statsd
        li High performance API extensions using Redis's Lua support
        li Search for jobs in the Web UI

